Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:04.52,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:10.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to be by your side more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:15.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:36.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Flame of {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:36.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Flame of {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Enemy at the Snowy Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only the vice-captain at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Snake was the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was referred to as Enjya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in search of that man myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man who inflicted a wound upon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Flame Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to burn that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wish for!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the key to this surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're professionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheap tricks won't work against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone should rush in as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply rushing in won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need the enemy to focus only on that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring an end to this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun, lend me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just reminiscing gives me a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain who razed Dungletale was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He burned the village instantly, without any change in emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was attracted to him because of his perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I ambushed him form behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little mistake from the aberration that was my youth, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How strong is our captain? Is his strength real?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to confirm his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He burned me with ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you be using these for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep your hands moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that in your world, everyone is equally skilled at using all technologies, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with some studying and training, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take a look at your world one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are they going to make us wait? Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry, or else everyone will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, we'll go by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us stop talking about the past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send a messenger to Henrietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have her sign a pledge in which she promises to withdraw her troops from Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unconditional agreement to withdraw her troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to make Her Highness do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind having your cute students burn to ashes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun, when you... head eastwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you decide to go back to your world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you all wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to borrow everybody's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid method.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Julio-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the front line hears of this,\Nthey'll respond with a full-scale attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only cornering yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albion doesn't think enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you have a death wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our top priority is to rescue everyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother with the enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't fight with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brats...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our strategy worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, get everyone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche! Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since my eyes were burned, they couldn't sense light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you see, then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say snakes perceive prey via their temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:09:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I use flame, I started to get rather sensitive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell one person from another by their temperatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smell the scent of you burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from my student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, it's you, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the temperature I've been searching for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you! How nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've... lost your ability to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei was... the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} a teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I never saw you in any wars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've never imagined that you'd become a {\i1}teacher{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who were once called Enjya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En... jya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he was referred to as Enjya the Flame Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one that burned everything, woman and child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's the one who stole the light from both of my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of my captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you haven't lost your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... that's how it should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Zerbst. Take Miss Tabitha and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun, Miss Vallière, take everyone out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the spell to undo a rope is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it pure luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert is my foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who killed my father and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who took everything away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butt out, plebeian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no business with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous! Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to burn to death, Captain-dono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day I burn you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you, Captain-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.28,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}Kam {\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}Diela...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:06.70,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Kam {\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}Diela...{\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to become this strong because of my devotion towards exacting revenge upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.66,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}Dil {\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ryofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.53,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Dil {\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}Ryofu.{\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would expect this much from you, Flame Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer the inexperienced lad I once was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has surpassed yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no... d-different from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still... so full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waz Wagaraz Wagaruze Winde!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my village's rancour!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that day you burned Dungletale?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realised... my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived only to see this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For twenty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Zerbst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... move...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes-kun... has the... right... to... kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tye Gyoph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's strange, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any signs of an epidemic here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then that I realised... the sin I had committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that... obeying orders was... the correct... thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even during war... killing a person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes-kun, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... make this your last... and... stop killing... any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are to tell me this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes... sheathe your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found this when we were cleaning up Colbert's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Saito-kun, I am writing this letter with the\Nintention of giving it to you when you go to war."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should tell you this:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've once committed a sin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to atone for my sin, I've devoted myself to research.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Recently, a thought has been crossing my mind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and that thought is, "atoning for sin is impossible".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Saito-kun, I want you to promise me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get used to people dying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get used to fighting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get used to killing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito-kun, you've told me many stories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stories of the world that you came from.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see that world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please take me there some day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just rambling on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you never be able to forgive Colbert-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei wanted to go to your world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a strange person, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll freeze to death if we crash into a snowy mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Warm each other up with our body heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Enemy at the Snowy Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
